ople</a></h5><ul class="list"><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/theology/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Theology & Spirituality">Theology & Spirituality</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/ministry/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Church Life & Ministry">Church Life & Ministry</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/current-affairs/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Politics & Current Affairs">Politics & Current Affairs</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/higher-education/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Higher Education">Higher Education</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/books/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Books">Books</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/topics/s/science/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Science">Science</a></li><div class="js-editable" data-id="177" data-name="hot_topics" data-itemtype="channel" data-itemid="162"><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/people/p/c-rene-padilla/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category=" Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Hot Topics: C. René Padilla">C. Rene Padilla</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/topics/c/coronavirus/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category=" Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Hot Topics: Coronavirus">Coronavirus</a></li><li class="list-item"><a href="/ct/people/s/john-stott/" class="nav_link js-clickTrack" data-category=" Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Hot Topics: Stott, John">John Stott</a></li></div>
