<div class="article-byline "><span class="author" itemprop="author">MORGAN LEE</span><span class="pipe">|</span><span class="postdate" itemprop="datePublished"><time datetime="2021-8-23">23/agosto/2021 </time></span></div>
<div class="article-languages spacer-top-5"><span class="lang-switcher spacer-right-20 spacer-top-5"><a href="/news/2021/august/pray-for-haiti-earthquake-2021-2010-christians-theodicy.html" class="" title="English">English</a></span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="article-featured-image "><div class="container"><figure class="p-relative align-center spacer-top-40"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/125237.png?w=940" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/125237.png?w=1880 2x" width="940" alt="Cómo orar por Haití después de otro terremoto letal" title="Cómo orar por Haití después de otro terremoto letal" /></figure><figcaption class="spacer-top-5 spacer-bottom-5"><div class="credit ">
									Image:
									
										Reginald Louissaint Jr. / AFP / Getty Images
									</div>
<div class="caption spacer-top-10 ">Un hombre camina frente a una iglesia en Les Anglais, Haití, destrozada el pasado 14 de agosto en un terremoto.</div>
</figcaption></div></section><section class="container"><div class="spacer-top-25 u-cf social-nav-item">
				<div
					class="ctSocialShare ctSocialShare_horizontal ctSocialShare_fallback"
